descriptors.name: Downy Rinse & Refresh Laundry Fabric Rinse, Cool Cotton, 3 ct., 76.5 fl. oz.
descriptors.shortDescription:
• 3 bottles per pack, 25.5 fl. oz. each, totaling 76.5 fl. oz.
  • Infused with cool cotton scents
  • Designed for use as a laundry detergent booster to enhance the freshness and softness of fabrics
  • Effectively rinses away residues, leaving fabrics softer and brighter than using detergent alone
  • Specialized in removing stubborn odors from fabrics
descriptors.longDescription:
Revolutionize Your Laundry Routine

Transform your washing experience with the Downy Rinse & Refresh Laundry Odor Remover and Fabric Softener. This innovative product replaces your traditional liquid softener, delivering an enhanced clean and a delightful, light aroma to your clothing. Thanks to its breakthrough technology, the Downy Rinse & Refresh washes away residues and odors trapped within fabrics, leaving them smelling fresh and feeling soft.

Superior Odor and Residue Removal

Downy Rinse & Refresh is powered by 3x the odor powder, which effectively eliminates smelly residues from your fabrics. While traditional liquid fabric softeners can leave residues that trap odors, Downy Rinse and Refresh acts as a laundry detergent booster, doing all the hard work for you and ensuring your clothes come out smelling great.

Delightful Freshness

Experience the light, refreshing scent of Cool Cotton with each wash. The Downy Rinse & Refresh is perfect for reviving smelly activewear, musty towels, or even laundry left in your washing machine overnight. Forget about re-washing clothes with vinegar or other homemade laundry hacks, this detergent booster strips away those pesky odors, leaving your clothes smelling fresh and clean.

Gentle and Safe for All Fabrics

Downy Rinse & Refresh Laundry Odor Remover and Fabric Softener is free of dyes and heavy perfumes, making it gentle on sensitive skin and perfect for baby clothes. It's safe for all types of fabrics, so you can use it with confidence on all your laundry items.

Easy to Use

Using Downy Rinse & Refresh is a breeze. Simply start with your usual detergent, then add the Downy Rinse & Refresh during the rinse cycle. You can either fill the fabric softener dispenser or pour it directly into the machine. For an extra boost of freshness, pair it with any Downy Scent Booster Beads in your laundry routine.

BROWSE.freightMessage:
Freight shipping
Items that are large or heavy ship with a freight carrier. When your order is ready, the carrier contacts you to set up a delivery time. Delivery times are usually within a 4-hour window Monday-Friday, between 8am and 5pm.

Currently, we have three types of freight delivery: Threshold, Commercial and White Glove.

Threshold: The carrier contacts you to set up a delivery time. The items are delivered to the first dry area available. For example, your front entryway or garage.

Commercial: The carrier contacts you to set up a delivery time. The items are delivered to a commercial business with access to a loading dock. The member needs to unload the truck.

White Glove: Carrier offering differs by product but can include services such as delivery, installation within the home, and removal of old product. Details about a specific product can be found on the product page.


Some carriers offer additional services. These services may require payment and are paid directly to the carrier.
